# EduAI-SA Vision 2035

## Our Vision

By 2035, EduAI-SA will be Africa's leading AI-powered education platform, helping millions of learners unlock their potential while empowering teachers, supporting parents, and strengthening schools.

---

# Our Dream

We believe every child deserves the opportunity to learn, regardless of where they live or their circumstances.

We believe every teacher deserves intelligent tools that reduce administrative work and increase time spent teaching.

We believe parents should be active partners in their children's education.

Artificial Intelligence should support human potential—not replace it.

---

# What Success Looks Like

Millions of learners using EduAI-SA.

Hundreds of thousands of teachers saving valuable time.

Parents actively engaged in their children's learning.

Schools making data-driven decisions to improve educational outcomes.

South African innovation making a positive impact across Africa.

